description: The NEOS Enhanced Income Aggregate Bond ETF (BNDI) seeks monthly income in a tax-efficient manner by investing in a representative portfolio of the U.S. Aggregate Bond Market and employing a data-driven put option strategy. Actively managed by NEOS, the fund aims to take advantage of tax loss harvesting opportunities and generate additional income from the sale of SPX Index options.
name: Neos Enhanced Income Aggregate Bond ETF
